d an existing bug in WebRender. If the contents of a blob image go out of view WebRender won't remember them and it only asks for the newly invalid region. i.e. If we don't clip our rendering to the dirty rect the items don't go away.", "author": "jmuizelaar@mozilla.com", "id": 13300448, "time": "2018-05-23T19:29:14Z"}, {"text": "I've filed https://github.com/servo/webrender/issues/2771 about this.", "author": "jmuizelaar@mozilla.com", "id": 13301935, "time": "2018-05-23T22:39:44Z"}, {"text": "Batch updating status flags based on WR schedule - please adjust if needed.", "author": "dbolter@mozilla.com", "id": 13361994, "time": "2018-05-24T20:06:33Z"}, {"text": "This is fixed now.", "author": "bugmail@mozilla.staktrace.com", "id": 13389043, "time": "2018-06-05T19:43:35Z"}], "id": 1463792, "priority": "P1", "cc": ["a.beingessner@gmail.com", "bugmail@mozilla.staktrace.com", "jan@ikenmeyer.eu", "mcastelluccio@mozilla.com"], "cf_crash_signature": "", "version": "unspecified", "is_cc_accessible": true, "cf_tracking_firefox_esr52": "---", "see_also": ["https://github.com/servo/webrender/issues/2771"], "cf_tracking_thunderbird_esr60": "---", "cf_platform_rel": "---", "product": "Core", "cf_fx_iteration": "---", "blocks": [1386665, 1458968], "qa_contact": "", "creation_time": "2018-05-23T16:37:24Z", "cf_status_firefox_esr52": "unaffected", "component": "Graphics: WebRender", "assigned_to_detail": {"email": "bugmail@mozilla.staktrace.com", "id": 426788, "name": "bugmail@mozilla.staktrace.com", "real_name": "Kartikaya Gupta (email:kats@mozilla.com)"}, "cf_tracking_firefox_esr60": "---", "cf_status_firefox62": "fixed", "cf_status_firefox61": "disabled", "cf_status_firefox60": "disabled", "target_milestone": "mozilla62", "cf_rank": null, "cf_qa_whiteboard": "", "severity": "normal", "groups": [], "cf_status_thunderbird_esr52": "---", "url": "", "cf_status_thunderbird_esr60": "---", "creator_detail": {"email": "jmuizelaar@mozilla.com", "id": 309398, "name": "jmuizelaar@mozilla.com